Welcome to Day 3 of the 2025 PUBG MOBILE GLOBAL CHAMPIONSHIP Group Green!
The chase for the Grand Finals continues now. Legends rise, nerves break, and every moment could change a team’s destiny.
The road to the Grand Finals gets tougher with each match so buckle up, grab your snacks, and get ready for another day of world-class PUBG MOBILE action! 🏆🔥

This year’s format has been reworked to deliver even more thrill both for fans and for the teams chasing glory.

The first big twist was The Gauntlet. 
16 of the world’s best-qualified teams faced off with high stakes. 
The stakes? Massive.
Rank 1–7: Advanced straight to the Grand Finals.
Rank 8–16: Got one more shot through the Group Stage.

In each group, only the top 3 advance directly to the Grand Finals.
Teams finishing 4th–11th get one last shot in the Last Chance stage.
But those landing 12th–16th? Their 2025 PMGC journey ends there.

Finally, the Last Chance (Dec 6–7) brings everything to the edge.
Two days. Two tickets.
Finish in the top 2, or watch the Grand Finals from the sidelines.

द्युम्वान - द्युम्वान भगवान शंकर का सातवाँ अवतार माना जाता है और इस अवतार की शक्ति माता द्युमावती मानी जाती हैं।

मातंग - मातंग भगवान शंकर का नौवां अवतार है और इस अवतार की शक्ति माता मातंगी मानी जाती हैं। इस अवतार में ब्रह्मदेव के सभी गुण मौजूद हैं।
